Algerian Tractors Company ATC Spa, bụ ụlọ ọrụ jikọrọ aka pụrụ iche na mmepe nke igwe ọrụ ugbo
Emepụtara ya na August 16, 2012 mgbe nkwekọrịta n'etiti ụlọ ọrụ Algerian Etrag na American Group AGCO
Ụlọ ọrụ ahụ na-emepụta traktọ na El Khroub, nke dị nso na Constantine, Algeria.
Etrag mechiri mmekọrịta ụlọ ọrụ na azụmahịa na AGCO, onye ndu ụwa na mmepụta nke igwe ọrụ ugbo. Ha mepụtara na 16 Ọgọstụ 2012 otu njikọ aka (njikọ ọrụ) a na-akpọ Algerian Tractors Company ATC Spa
Nkwekọrịta ahụ nwere ndị mmekọ mpaghara abụọ: ETRAG na (36%), Pmat na (15%) na AGCO na (41%).
Ụlọ ọrụ ahụ na-emepụta otu traktọ Etrag na ọtụtụ traktọ Massey Ferguson.
